    <item>
      <title>苏格兰民族党试图重建，斯温尼当选苏格兰首席部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/swinney-elected-scotland-first-minister-as-snp-tries-to-rebuild</link>
      <description><![CDATA[约翰·斯温尼 (John Swinney) 当选苏格兰首席部长，他领导的执政党苏格兰民族党力图在预计于今年下半年举行的英国全国投票之前阻止民意调查的长期下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/swinney-elected-scotland-first-minister-as-snp-tries-to-rebuild</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 14:44:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列逼近拉法，谈判陷入僵局，局势高度紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/israel-edges-into-rafah-with-tensions-high-over-deadlocked-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列控制进入埃及的拉法口岸的举动引发了对其最终目标的激烈争论：这是长期威胁入侵加沙南部城市的开始，还是试图向哈马斯施压，要求放宽停火条件以及释放人质？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/israel-edges-into-rafah-with-tensions-high-over-deadlocked-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 14:31:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>盖洛普发现鲍威尔的公众信心接近历史低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/powell-s-public-confidence-nears-historic-lows-gallup-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的盖洛普民意调查显示，由于通货膨胀持续存在且高物价激怒了美国消费者，杰罗姆·鲍威尔正在努力摆脱近四分之一个世纪以来评级最低的美联储主席的标签。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/powell-s-public-confidence-nears-historic-lows-gallup-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 14:29:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称校园抗议中“不允许反犹太主义”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/biden-to-decry-campus-antisemitism-in-holocaust-memorial-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，在一年一度的大屠杀纪念活动期间针对以色列的校园抗议活动中“没有反犹太主义的容身之地”，他直接应对了威胁分裂其政治联盟的示威活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/biden-to-decry-campus-antisemitism-in-holocaust-memorial-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 09:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
